org.anchoranalysis.io.output.bean.rules

Class IgnoreUnderscorePrefixUnless

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<OutputEnabledRules>
      • OutputEnabledRules
        • OutputEnableRulesSpecify
          • IgnoreUnderscorePrefixUnless

  • public class IgnoreUnderscorePrefixUnless
extends OutputEnableRulesSpecify
    Like IgnoreUnderscorePrefix for all first and level-outputs unless a particular outputs are explicitly specified.

    If first-level are specified, this takes precedence, and only these outputs are allowed.

    Similarly if any particular second-level outputs are specified, these replace IgnoreUnderscorePrefix.

    Otherwise IgnoreUnderscorePrefix is used.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
